Return a pre-compiled, PK/PD model.

Return a pre-compiled, PK/PD model.

house(...)

Arguments

...
passed to update

Value

A packmod object, ready to simulate.

Examples


mod <- mrgsolve:::house()
#> Warning: cannot open compressed file 'C:\Users\devin\Documents\Repos\mrgsolve/project/housemodel.RDS', probable reason 'No such file or directory'
#> Error in gzfile(file, "rb"): cannot open the connection

see(mod)
#> 
#> Model file:  demo.cpp 
#>  
#>  $GLOBAL
#>  #define CP (CENT/VC)
#>  #define INH (CP/(IC50+CP))
#>  
#>  $SET delta=0.1
#>  
#>  $PARAM TVCL=1, TVVC=20, KA = 1.3, KIN=100, KOUT=2, IC50=10
#>  
#>  $CMT GUT, CENT, RESP
#>  
#>  $MAIN
#>    double CL = exp(log(TVCL) + ETA(1));
#>    double VC = exp(log(TVVC) + ETA(2));
#>  
#>    RESP_0 = KIN/KOUT;
#>  
#>  $OMEGA 0 0
#>  
#>  $ODE
#>    dxdt_GUT = -KA*GUT;
#>    dxdt_CENT = KA*GUT - (CL/VC)*CENT;
#>    dxdt_RESP = KIN*(1-INH) - KOUT*RESP;
#>  
#>  $CAPTURE CP
#>   

mod %>% ev(amt=100) %>% mrgsim %>% plot
